alerts.title: Lake Wind Advisory
alerts.description:
...LAKE WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM NOON TODAY TO 4 AM EDT
TUESDAY...
The National Weather Service in Columbia has issued a Lake Wind
Advisory, which is in effect from noon today to 4 AM EDT Tuesday.
* TIMING...This afternoon and tonight.
* WINDS...Southeast to South winds 15 to 25 knots, with gusts up
to 30 knots, this afternoon. Southwest winds 15 to 25 knots,
with gusts up to 30 knots, tonight. Higher gusts near
thunderstorms.
* IMPACTS...Strong wind and rough chop will create hazardous
conditions on area lakes.
